{"tid":1657604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李慧琼批評施政報告欠缺具體回應處理目前混亂情況","createTime":"2019-10-16T07:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T07:55:52.000Z","uid":40667,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7963e90843c6efbec3d268ff616ccaac4c5b1976","tid":1657604,"uid":40667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"民建聯回應特首林鄭月娥新一份施政報告，主席李慧琼表示，社會現時紛亂，但施政報告未能符合市民及民建聯的期望，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">形容施政因循守舊，困局無力突破</span></span>，批評當局欠缺具體回應，來處理目前混亂情況。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼說，政府在土地供應方面提出具體措施，包括提出引用《收回土地條例》，雖然市民未必感受到有希望，但認同不可能只透過一份施政報告就能處理。<br />\n<br />\n議員柯創盛批評施政報告在房屋方面「唔湯唔水」，質疑當局提出加快出售39個租置屋邨未售出單位的措施，達不到居民需求，議員梁志祥就質疑政府在褔利方面的建議措施，只有如「仙女散花」，可謂交白卷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486516-20191016.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486516-20191016.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=b77fadb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486516-20191016.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=864ff358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486516-20191016.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">吓?! 選舉近了</span>"},{"pid":"9ad19bc92645c3869353c6888c43c5e7a64bcaae","tid":1657604,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c3ab0f71ce9b1c260c8e23bb22b6822c3fc48f66","tid":1657604,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"民建聯係咪作反！不做實事！香港值得更好的建設派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a